Disease: The type of disease or illness the individual has been diagnosed with
Fever: Whether the individual has a fever (Yes/No)
Cough: Whether the individual has a cough (Yes/No)
Fatigue: Whether the individual is experiencing fatigue (Yes/No)
Difficulty Breathing: Whether the individual is experiencing difficulty breathing (Yes/No)
Blood Pressure: The blood pressure level of the individual (e.g. Low, Normal, High)
Cholesterol Level: The cholesterol level of the individual (e.g. Low, Normal, High)
Outcome Variable: The outcome of the disease diagnosis (Positive/Negative)
